=========================
Map Information
=========================

This map is a work in progress, Im creating a new version from what the public has suggested.
I will leave this map as it is and will release another version soon.


The Mansion based on the Resident Evil Game by Capcom.
It has secret hiding spots, a special Panic Room for those that do not like to mess with the zombies. Doors Should be destryable.
Enjoy the map and have fun.

Special Thanks to JonThePudding from Singapore (you know how u are),
For helping me test my map.

And A SPECIAL Thanks to The {GiLa} SG Zombie Server, That Inspired me to make my very first zombie map. 
AND Very very very up most very special thank YOU to {GiLa} Nagios.. (hope i got it spelled right)
